      <title>杰富瑞称，RWE 首席执行官引发股票回购希望</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/rwe-chief-sparks-hopes-for-share-buyback-jefferies-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据杰富瑞金融集团 (Jefferies Financial Group Inc.) 的销售交易报告显示，德国莱茵集团 (RWE AG) 管理层暗示，在股价表现不佳后，该能源公司可能考虑回购股票以安抚投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-27/rwe-chief-sparks-hopes-for-share-buyback-jefferies-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 27 Sep 2024 09:39:42 GMT</pubDate>
